item.title: You Won't Believe What's Inside These Blackpink 'How You Like That' Photocards!
item.description: Introduction K-pop fans around the world have been eagerly awaiting the release of Blackpink’s new single, “How You Like That,” and the group certainly delivered But what many fans may not know is that the single also came with a special set of photocards featuring never-before-seen photos and artwork of the group In this blog post, we’ll take a look at what’s inside the special Blackpink “How You Like That” photocards and why fans should consider collecting them
